title: Sheriff's office received 20 calls about Florida shooting suspect
text:
Sheriff's office received 20 calls about Florida shooting suspect 4:25am IST - 02:13 
The sheriff of Broward County where the Florida school shooting took place said in a Friday press conference that authorities had received around 20 ''calls for service'' in the last few years regarding the Florida shooting suspect.
